      <h1>Interesting Pins Just for Parents</h1>
      
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>This is a purely front end build out of all the pages, modals, and states needed to create ParentPins core site. Includes html, css, and javascript. Will later convert to Ruby on Rails using Haml/Sass.</p>
      <p>This site is basically Pinterest for parents interested in great finds for to help their children. ParentPins uses the concept of 4 buckets of Pins; Article, Gift, Idea and General Pin types. ParentPins also has a very small taxonomy applied which creates top level categories to be used in search and general board browsing.</p>
      <p>Will be monetized through the use of <a href="http://www.skimlinks.com/" title="link out to html5 boilerplate site">skimlinks.com</a> API product feed in order to supply an onsite store with products.</p>
      
